animeTitle: Soukyuu no Fafner: Behind the Line
otherNames: Soukyuu no Fafner: Dead Aggressor - Behind the Line;  蒼穹のファフナー BEHIND THE LINE
synopsis: Announced at the Soushi Minashiro Birthday Fes 2021. Initially promised to fans during the 2017 birthday event, this self-contained entry to the Fafner series will be a "peaceful spinoff".
